{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 14:43:17.840577", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission accepted.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"leaf_router_0_0\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"host_static_blackhole\"]\n\nRecommended next actions (optional, not submitted):\n- On leaf_router_0_0, inspect static routes: e.g., ip route show | grep 10.0.0.0\n- Remove the unintended blackhole: e.g., ip route del blackhole 10.0.0.0/30\n- Verify route table then verify connectivity from pc_0_0 (ping, tcpdump) and check interface counters.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2441, "output_tokens": 130, "total_tokens": 2571, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
